#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Times_available" field of the "Staff" table</h2>
This field will be used to determine what routes a particular staff member could drive, but is
currently unused at least by the software and the format is not specified yet.  Coordinators
may use it for their own notes, but beware:  the format is likely to change if automatic driver
allocation is enabled.

